org.jamsim.r
Class RDataFrame

java.lang.Object
  org.jamsim.r.RDataFrame
All Implemented Interfaces:
net.casper.data.model.CBuilder
public class RDataFrame
extends Object
implements net.casper.data.model.CBuilder

An R expression that is an R dataframe. The dataframe "names" attribute is used for the column headings. Implements CBuilder.
